title: The Best of the Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of the Dan Patrick Show
description:
Covino and Rich fill in for Dan Patrick and the crew, and they dive right into their morning routines, specifically both share what it takes to be an early bird in the gym. Plus, the guys debate fair-weather fans and want to know if your team is getting blown out, should you still watch?

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
